svg.title: Bouwanndeel
svg.desc: Bouwaandeel offers project developers and other initiators access to private capital. We offer project developers and planners a platform to present their plans to the rest of the Netherlands. Every project is carefully checked by us for quality, financial proposition and feasibility. Our secure digital environment makes it possible for private individuals to invest both small and large amounts in real estate projects. With Bouwaandeel we want to stimulate desired developments in your living environment. By investing through our platform you help with this and you receive a return on your investment.
